# Documentation — docs/ is team-internal by default; only the paths
# explicitly un-ignored below ship with the repo.
#   docs/architecture.md             — judge-facing architecture detail
#   docs/runbooks/demo-recording.md  — AC5 runbook referenced by README
# Everything else (spec / features / decisions / design / dev-commands /
# testing / product / conventions / archive) stays local.
docs/*
!docs/architecture.md
!docs/runbooks/

# Node / TypeScript
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
out/
coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# Env / secrets
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
*.key
*.pem

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Logs
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

# rules
AGENTS.md
CLAUDE.md

# runtime artifacts (generated meme images from demo runs)
apps/server/tmp/